      {"speaker": "陈明", "chinese": "我建议你去四川。成都和峨嵋山这两个地方非去不可。", "pinyin": "Wǒ jiànyì nǐ qù sìchuān. Chéngdū hé éméi shān zhè liǎng ge dìfang fēi qù búkě.", "english": "I suggest you go to Sichuan. Chengdu and Mount Emei are must-sees."},
